Difference between document and window


 Document 
It represents any HTML document or wed page that is loaded in the browser
It is loaded inside the window
It is the object of window
We can access the document from a window using the window document
The document is part of browser object model and document object model
Properties of document object such as title,body etc can also be accessed by a window like this window document title
example:content  in the window like paragraph,images etc


Window 
It represents a browser window or frame that displays the contents of the webpage 
It is the very first object that is loaded in the browser
It is the object that is loaded in the browser 
Global object, functions and variables of js are members of the window object
We can access the window from the window only 
The window is part of BOM not DOM 
Example : opening new tab 
                    History
                    Download 
                    Email,  etc

